rows.label: bf05170100_0010
rows.name: You're pretty good, boy.

rows.label: bf05170100_0020
rows.name: Right back at you. Impressive!

rows.label: bf05170100_0030
rows.name:
I never thought there'd be another Driver and Blade
besides Meleph and Kagutsuchi like this.

rows.label: bf05170100_0040
rows.name:
You're still not using it, are you?
The power of the Holy Grail.

rows.label: bf05170100_0050
rows.name: I only use Hikari's power against bad guys.

rows.label: bf05170100_0060
rows.name:
What are you saying?
Are you trying to say I'm a good person?

rows.label: bf05170100_0070
rows.name: Am I wrong?

rows.label: bf05170100_0080
rows.name: You've got some nerve, boy!

rows.label: bf05170100_0090
rows.name: As expected of the Holy Grail's Driver.

rows.label: bf05170100_0100
rows.name: Is that sufficient, Zeke-sama?

rows.label: bf05170100_0110
rows.name: Sure, you pass.

rows.label: bf05170100_0115
rows.name:
These guys probably won't casue any truoble
if you let them into the Holy See.

rows.label: bf05170100_0120
rows.name: What... was that?!

rows.label: bf05170100_0130
rows.name:
I've been involved with the Holy See for years now.
Well, I'm something like a special envoy.

rows.label: bf05170100_0140
rows.name: I heard that the Holy Grail had awakened, you see.

rows.label: bf05170100_0145
rows.name: So I volunteered to check things out.

rows.label: bf05170100_0150
rows.name: Sorry for testing you like this.

rows.label: bf05170100_0160
rows.name:
We were planning on getting this
over with in ONE encounter.

rows.label: bf05170100_0170
rows.name:
It's just that our prince here
has incredibly bad luck.

rows.label: bf05170100_0180
rows.name: Ah, I kind of get it.

rows.label: bf05170100_0190
rows.name:
What are you talking about?
That was just coincidence, just coincidence...

rows.label: bf05170100_0200
rows.name: Ah!

rows.label: bf05170100_0210
rows.name: Why me?!

rows.label: bf05170100_0220
rows.name: There he goes.

rows.label: bf05170100_0230
rows.name: Hmmm...bad luck indeed.

rows.label: bf05170100_0240
rows.name: Um, shouldn't we go help him?

rows.label: bf05170100_0250
rows.name:
Don't worry. He'll probably make 
his way back on his own soon enough.

rows.label: bf05170100_0260
rows.name: Let's just board the ship!
